                        <title>Prayers of the middle of the night</title>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="7v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3522Epistle">First Epistle to the Thessalonians</ref> 4:14-5:10</title>
                        <note>
                           The verse <q xml:lang="gez">ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ጥዑመ፡ ስም፡ ዘጸዋዕኮ፡ ለጰውሎስ፡ ጸውዓነ፡ ውስተ፡ ከብካብከ።</q> is added on <locus target="#8v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="9r"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3507Epistle">First Epistle of Peter</ref> 5:5-11</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ኦዘለከ፡ ተውህበከ፡ 
                                 <sic>መራኁተ፡</sic>
                               ዘመንግሥተ፡ 
                                 <sic>ሰማያተ።</sic>
                               
                           ኰኵሐ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ አርኅወነ፡ ንባዕ፡ ቤተ፡ መርዓሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፨</q> is added on <locus target="#9v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="9v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1019Actsof">Gǝbra ḥawāryāt</ref> 16:30-34</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">ስቡሕ፡ አንተ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ወመንክር፡ ስነ፡ ስብሐቲከ፡</q> is added on <locus target="#10r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1558Matthew">Wangel za-Mātewos</ref> 25:1-13</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">
                              
                                 <sic>ርስየነ፡</sic>
                               ድልዋነ፡ ንትቀበል፡ ከመ፡ መርዓዊ፡ በዘይተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ <add place="margin">ጥሉል፡</add>
                           </q> 
                           is added on <locus target="#11r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1793Leviti">Leviticus</ref> 23:1-8</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">እስመ፡ 
                                 <sic>ውእቱ፡</sic>
                               ዘወሀበ፡ ሕገ፡ ለሙሴ፡ ሰነብታቲሁ፡ ረሰየ፡ ለክብር፡ ወለውዳሴ፡</q> is added on 
                           <locus target="#11v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                        <locus from="12v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</ref> 5:1-18</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ረ<supplied reason="omitted">ስ</supplied>የነ፡ ድልዋነ፡ ከመ፡ ንባዕ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰንበተ፡ ሰበታቲሁ፡ ምስለ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ቅዱሳኒከ፡ ከመ፡ 
                              ንኩን፡ 
                                 <sic>ጽዋዓነ፡</sic>
                               ለበዓልከ፡</q> is added on <locus target="#14"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8">
                        <locus from="14v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3516Epistle">First Epistle to the Corinthians</ref> 15:51-16:2</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">
                              <supplied reason="omitted">ጥ</supplied>ዑመ፡ ልሳን፡ ምዑዝ፡ ከመ፡ ዕጣን፡ ጳውሎስ፡ መርሐ፡ ዕውራን፡ ዘበጽንፈ፡ ልብስከ፡ 
                              
                                 <sic>የሐይው፡</sic>
                               ዱያን፡</q> is added on <locus target="#15"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9">
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3509Epistle">First Epistle of John</ref> 1:1-5</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ዕፀ፡ አርዝ፡ ኀበ፡ ሙሐዘ፡ ማይ፡ ዘበቈለ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አሕመልመለ።</q> is added on <locus target="#15v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1019Actsof">Gǝbra ḥawāryāt</ref> 16:30-34</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">አንቅዕተ፡ ሕግ፡ ዘወንጌል፡ አፍላግ፡ አዕጹቀ፡ ዘይት፡ ወዘወይን፡ ኃረግ፨</q> is added on <locus target="#16r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                        <locus from="16v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</ref> 3:1-8</title>
                        <note>
                           The praise <q xml:lang="gez">ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፨ ኮከብ፡ ሰመይናከ፡ ፀሓየ፡ ጽድቅ፡</q> is added on <locus target="#17"/>.
                        </note>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
                        <title>Praises to God</title>
                        <note>
                           The praises include a passage on the vision of Ezekiel, beginning as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ርኢክዎ፡ ይብል፡ ነቢይ፡ ሕዝቅኤል፡ በላዔ፡ 
                              
                                 <sic>መጻሕድት፡</sic>
                              
                           </q>.
                        </note>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13">
                        <locus from="22r"/>
                        <title>Praise to Our Lady Mary</title>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ በአርያም፡ በውስተ፡ ውሳጤ፡ መንጦላዕት፡
                        </incipit>
                     </msItem>
