                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.24">
                        <locus from="32v"/>
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3519Epistle">Epistle to the Ephesians</ref> 6:10-24</title>
                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ኦነቅዓ፡ ጥበብ፡ ልሳነ፡ ዕፍረት፡ ጳውሎስ፡ አስተምህር፡ ለነ፡ ሰአልናከ፡ ሃ<supplied reason="explanation">ሌ፡ ሉያ፡</supplied> 
                              ሃ<supplied reason="explanation">ሌ፡ ሉያ፡</supplied> ሃ<supplied reason="explanation">ሌ፡ ሉያ፡</supplied> ከመ፡ ንትሉ፡ ንሕነ፡ አሠረ፡ ትምህርትከ፡ 
                           ወንርከብ፡ መክፈልተ፡ ውስተ፡ ርስትከ፨</q> is added on <locus target="#33v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
