                        <note>
                           The invocation <q xml:lang="gez">ኦዘርእስከ፡ መልዕልተ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ክቡር፡ መክብበ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</q> is added on <locus target="#34r"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.26">
                        <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1019Actsof">Gǝbra ḥawāryāt</ref> 12:6-11</title>
                        <note>
                           The passage <q xml:lang="gez">ሃሌ፡ ሉ<supplied reason="omitted">ያ፡</supplied> ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ከዋክብት፡ ብሩሃን፡ ሐዋርያት፡ መምህራን፡ ሰአሉ፡ ለነ፡ ስርየተ፡ ለኃጥአን፨</q> 
                           is added on <locus target="#34v"/>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
